Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼 真痛 真是一记好拳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:22:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别怕 来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.42,0:22:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.99,0:23:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐你又把猫带回家 会被爸爸骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.01,0:23:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 没办法了 我也帮忙跟爸爸说说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.20,0:23:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
